Software:
# When comes to software its what u see on a virtual screen may be OS(Operating system), apps or files.
And whats the third category?? yas Firmware and whats so special about that is it connects both hardware and software like a bridge, well 
will see that in coming section.

Firmware:
# As I mentioned ealrier it acts as a bypass between hardware and software but HOW? 
# when u switch on a pc basicaslly u first switch the CPU but before there is simple concept called bootloader ->BIOS/UEFI
BIOS(Both input-output system)-An old bootloader which comes into play when u swicth on the pc, the firmware checks the environment of the 
hardware is Good and after completing POST(post operating system test) it tells the driver to bootload or in ur terms loads the computers 
interface or OS.






  
  
  
